Because of the wording in the question,
it's possible for anyone to be confused.

146
00:11:02,828 --> 00:11:03,663
Sir.

147
00:11:05,164 --> 00:11:06,749
Just say you're sorry.

148
00:11:08,125 --> 00:11:09,502
Admit that you're ashamed.

149
00:11:18,135 --> 00:11:19,553
