150
00:11:19,637 --> 00:11:21,722
regarding whether or not

151
00:11:21,806 --> 00:11:25,101
our society is led by high achievers

152
00:11:25,184 --> 00:11:26,644
with top grades.

153
00:11:26,727 --> 00:11:29,271
In conclusion, it's important
to cultivate people of talent

154
00:11:29,355 --> 00:11:30,564
in various areas--

155
00:11:45,371 --> 00:11:47,873
