was vacant for a long time.

169
00:13:35,564 --> 00:13:38,025
But Choe Jun-u

170
00:13:38,275 --> 00:13:40,486
was recently elected
as our class vice president.

171
00:13:40,569 --> 00:13:43,864
Let's give him a big round of
applause to show him our support.

172
00:13:45,324 --> 00:13:48,035
